CS 468: Network Security : Spring 2021 <br />
CS 568: Advanced Computer Security and Online Privacy : Fall 2020 <br />   <!--[Fall 2020](https://www.cs.uic.edu/~polakis/classes/CS568/fall-2020/) <br>-->
CS 494: Network Security : Spring 2019, Spring 2020<br />
CS 194: Intro to CyberSecurity : Fall 2019 <br />
ENGR 194: Intro to CyberSecurity : Fall 2017, Fall 2018<br />
CS 377: Communication and Ethical Issues in Computing : Spring 2017<br /> <!--<a href="https://sites.google.com/site/uiccsethicsspring17/home">Spring 2017</a> <br> -->
CS 594: Security and Privacy in the Age of the Social Web : Fall 2016, Spring 2018</p>

